</p>
<p>So why do we care about having a product admin area? It's not just so we can click links and fill out
boxes. Nobody cares about that. The true reason to go in there is to control the products on the
frontend. So let's say just that:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="b35e47ba49">
